In 2010 the [[Los Angeles Film Critics Association Awards]] gave him a Career Achievement award.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.lafca.net/years/2009.htm ]{{dead link|date=August 2017}}&lt;/ref&gt; Belmondo attended the ceremony and made appearances in the Los Angeles area.

==Personal life==
On December 4, 1952, Belmondo married Élodie Constantin,&lt;ref&gt;{{cite book|author=Thomas Riggs|title=Contemporary Theatre, Film and Television, Volume 31|year=2000|publisher=Gale / Cengage Learning|isbn=0787646369|page=25}}&lt;/ref&gt; with whom he had three children: Patricia (1953–1993), who was killed in a fire, Florence (born 1958) and [[Paul Belmondo|Paul]] (born 1963). Belmondo and Constantin separated in 1965. She filed for divorce in September 1966, and it was finalized on January 5, 1968.&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|url=http://www.newspapers.com/newspage/382541800/|title=The Los Angeles Times from Los Angeles, California on January 6, 1968 · 16|website=Newspapers.com}}&lt;/ref&gt;

He had relationships with [[Ursula Andress]] from 1965 to 1972,&lt;ref&gt;Earl Wilson (16 July 1972). [https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&amp;dat=19720716&amp;id=Lj4gAAAAIBAJ&amp;sjid=nGYEAAAAIBAJ&amp;pg=5184,967490&amp;hl=en It Happened Last Night]. ''[[Sarasota Herald-Tribune]]''.&lt;/ref&gt; [[Laura Antonelli]] from 1972 to 1980,&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.allocine.fr/article/fichearticle_gen_carticle=18643775.html Mort de Laura Antonelli, star italienne des années 1970 et ex-femme de Jean-Paul Belmondo] ''AlloCiné''; 22 June 2015.&lt;/ref&gt; Brazilian actress and singer Carlos Sotto Mayor from 1980 to 1987,&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|url=https://www.purepeople.com/article/carlos-sotto-mayor-l-ex-de-bebel-revient-en-bombe-atomique-avec-un-prince_a67735/1|title=Carlos Sotto Mayor : L'ex de Bébel revient en bombe atomique... avec un prince !|website=Purepeople.com}}&lt;/ref&gt; and Barbara Gandolfi from 2008 to 2012.&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|url=https://www.purepeople.com/article/jean-paul-belmondo-escroque-son-ex-barbara-gandolfi-jugee_a213440/1|title=Jean-Paul Belmondo escroqué : Son ex Barbara Gandolfi jugée|website=Purepeople.com}}&lt;/ref&gt;

In 1989, Belmondo was in his mid-50s when he met 24-year-old dancer Natty Tardivel. The couple lived together for over a decade before marrying in 2002. On 13 August 2003, Tardivel gave birth to then 70-year-old Belmondo's fourth child, Stella Eva Angelina. Belmondo and Tardivel divorced in 2008.

